        "content": "<p>I'm thinking about <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"116122\">@simulacrum</span>'s feedback that the \"How to vision\" page is kind of wordy. I don't disagree. I added a <a href=\"https://nikomatsakis.github.io/wg-async-foundations/vision/how_to_vision/status_quo.html#tldr\">TL;DR</a> section to the \"htv: status quo\" and made the <a href=\"https://nikomatsakis.github.io/wg-async-foundations/vision/status_quo/template.html\">template punchier too</a>.</p>",
        "id": 230856577,
        "sender_full_name": "nikomatsakis",
        "timestamp": 1616071785
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>I'll make a PR with those changes. There's probably more that can be done, but this is easy.</p>",
